<p>
  <span class="nym">Godiva</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old English</span> <i>god</i> 'god, deity' + <span class="lang">Old English</span> <i>gifu</i> 'gift'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>The legend of the ride of Godiva, wife of Leofric earl of Mercia in the 11th C, first recorded in the 13th C, helped the name retain popularity after the Norman Conquest.</p>
</div>
  


